item.title: Webclient Generator
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

Why would you want code generated? Getting the code is fairly easy. Start with the proper tags, and you’re going to use an “applet” tag. Following that, you’ll be using the “param” tag for the startup args. Here’s a useful webpage that will help you: http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4.2/docs/guide/plugin/developer_guide/using_tags.html
